Therefore, I'm confident in my findings. The "Xã Ia Vê, Huyện Chư Prông, Tỉnh Gia Lai" address now falls under "Xã Ia Pia" with a high degree of certainty. I can now proceed to finalize the output with confidence, confident knowing that my approach to matching has been rigorous and meticulous.
